div.p:
China voluntarily to offer 4 concessions; 
                                1.

To employ Japanese officers as advisers to Chinese troops in
                                    South Manchuria and Eastern Mongolia;
                                2.

To employ Japanese military officers as instuctors in Chinese
                                    public schools;
                                3.

The Governor General at Mukden to go in person and apologize
                                    to the Japanese Governor General at Dairen and the Japanese
                                    Consul at Mukden;
                                4.

China to make monetary compensation to the families of
                                    Japanese killed at Chengchiatun;
